text: Jaroslav Hílek (born 6 June 1978) is a Slovak football player who currently plays for ŠK SFM Senec, on loan from FK Viktoria Žižkov . ==External links== * Profile at fcdac1904.com * Profile at iDNES.cz Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak footballers Category:FK Senica players Category:FC Spartak Trnava players Category:SK Dynamo České Budějovice players Category:FK Viktoria Žižkov players Category:Expatriate footballers in the Czech Republic Category:Czech First League players Category:FC DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda players Category:ŠK Senec players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Association football midfielders
